### Code Changes: Territory-Responsive Scrambler Scaling
- Modified `_pressure_budgets` in both `AnthropicPilotAgentPolicy` and `AlphaCogV2AgentPolicy`
- When losing territory (enemy_j > friendly_j + 2 after step 500), shift budget toward scramblers
  - 5+ agents: scrambler_budget = max(pressure_budget // 2, 1)
  - 4 agents: 1 aligner + 2 scramblers
  - 2 agents: 0 aligners + 1 scrambler
- Also lowered scrambler resource threshold when losing (min_res >= 3 instead of 5)
